{"tid":1630371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"出街發夢 咪撚再講睇車讓車","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:06.000Z","uid":163090,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc26ed2dd7ee812a5149e562129d38656185dc94","tid":1630371,"uid":163090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"我想講 次次出去發夢<br />\n畀狗追個陣 唔好再同我講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇車 同 讓車</span></span><br />\n我地係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤退</span></span>緊嫁<br />\n後面仲有一班手足退緊<br />\n我地係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">塞住</span></span>d車 阻住班狗衝<br />\n你地一個二個就叫人睇車讓車 讓你老母呀<br />\n我地讓完條路 畀車過左 d狗咪可以直接衝囉<br />\n成條馬路空哂 淨係得手足 d狗車仲唔衝呀<br />\n屌你老母 下次<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤退</span></span>個陣<br />\n麻煩大家可唔可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手做路障 唔畀d車行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畀後面手足行左先 人命關天呀</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地手足畀人拉到 係暴動罪嫁 要坐十年嫁</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班司機畀狗追 唔會有事嫁</span></span><br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩</span></span>答位手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以 幫手做人形唔障</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護手足緊要呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"598c86f039497fa94b5f6f6e82613b371a7cc4da","tid":1630371,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:20.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"154f378cae643cf6c4d83277beebe6bf64fecb16","